metadata.name: Angel inside of me
metadata.description: I am not just an angel, but a cupid, called to share love and light! I want to give as much happiness, my inner warmth and love as I can. But in order to have something to share, you have to find it in yourself! To allow yourself to be yourself, to recognize your uniqueness. To say to yourself, "I love!" One on one, just a pure heart and inner strength. They open the door to serenity and confidence! And now my heart is open to you because I accept myself!
